{"tid":2050670,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"美國據報最快周四將CCTV等中國官媒列外國使團 限制活動","createTime":"2020-06-04T09:19:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-04T14:53:04.000Z","uid":227801,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c8c685ae5d8439c940883a8a1580c624fdd4838b","tid":2050670,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T09:19:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1530164-20200604.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1530164-20200604.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=Fi4Me5dMHeyo7M%2BwlVraY6pJ2kzo9njAZIZZFH2Kh%2FI%3D&h=f8768302\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1530164-20200604.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=04763598\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1530164-20200604.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n路透社引述消息人士報道，美國最快當地星期四，將北京中央電視台及中新社等最少四間中國官方媒體，列為外國使團，預料勢必加劇中美緊張關係。<br />\n<br />\n美國在今年二月，已經將新華社等五間中國官媒列為外國使團，指控他們被中國政府利用作宣傳，他們必須向美國國務院登記僱員人數及在美國的物業。中國其後撤銷三間美國傳媒機構在華記者的記者證，並驅逐他們出境。<br />\n<br />\n白宮、美國國務院及中國駐華盛頓大使館，暫時未有回應。"},{"pid":"d6fc59f1fd84020309b3b9a256061ef76dac6c98","tid":2050670,"uid":227801,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T09:20:42.000Z","msg":"國情動向&nbsp;16:49&nbsp;2020/06/04&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n中美角力持續升級，媒體戰或升溫，繼美國將新華社等5間中國媒體列為「外國使團」後，路透引述知情人士稱，美國料最早周四（6月4日）將至少4間中國媒體機構，包括中央電視台（CCTV）及中國新聞社（中新社），列為「外國使團」，加大對其在美運作的限制。<br />\n報道指出，被列為「外國使團」的中國媒體，需向美國國務院提交在美工作人員的姓名、個人資料及人事變動決定，並向國務院登記在美租賃或持有的房產清單。<br />\n早於今年2月，美國把新華社、中國環球電視網（CGTN）、中國國際廣播電台（CRI）、《中國日報》發行公司和《人民日報》的美國總代理海天發展公司，共5間中國官媒企業列為「外國使團」，限制其在美運營。"},{"pid":"88dafc75098930c25bf0611b5ee0ad72180d5a79","tid":2050670,"uid":310700,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T09:22:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5B91egZ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5B91egZ.gif&h=65866fb7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"94c022d307a29c8f3de81eb4f2b137c1cae83a63","tid":2050670,"uid":156652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T09:24:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iED5FXG.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiED5FXG.gif&h=ad6b53ed&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9f7440b33837c23b7f317ba62cb9249bd0115517","tid":2050670,"uid":254383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T09:29:17.000Z","msg":"根本係間諜組織"},{"pid":"bc4b71e0ca3598ceb73062cd9dc64ac448598f3f","tid":2050670,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T09:30:09.000Z","msg":"中國：等出年拜登上台之後解除禁令 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cc2bee08cfbe74274657c565942574922f434ce","tid":2050670,"uid":225798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T09:31:22.000Z","msg":"列埋TVB 唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b8dc4e6e682fbdd35b74710837e020794803cd4","tid":2050670,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"bc4b71e0ca3598ceb73062cd9dc64ac448598f3f","tid":2050670,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T09:30:09.000Z","msg":"中國：等出年拜登上台之後解除禁令 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T09:32:19.000Z","msg":"Biden話左跟機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"218b3de870fe1e94c3d3fe6f600fda8b20f68c57","tid":2050670,"uid":271199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T09:43:37.000Z","msg":"應該加埋cctvb <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8258fc04c60c3450ade10197e4c95857c94bd83","tid":2050670,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T14:39:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee134f